<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Recognition shall only be given if the competent authority is satisfied that the institution's risk-management system is conceptually sound and implemented with integrity and that, in particular, the following qualitative standards are met: </inglise>
<eesti> Heakskiit antakse &uuml;ksnes siis, kui p&auml;dev asutus on veendunud, et asutuse riskijuhtimiss&uuml;steem on sisuliselt veatu, s&uuml;steemi rakendatakse terviklikult ja eelk&otilde;ige t&auml;idetakse j&auml;rgmisi kvaliteedin&otilde;udeid: </eesti>
<inglise> (i) the internal risk-measurement model is closely integrated into the daily risk-management process of the institution and serves as the basis for reporting risk exposures to senior management of the institution; </inglise>
<eesti> i) sisemine riskim&otilde;&otilde;tmismudel on tihedalt seotud asutuse igap&auml;evase riskijuhtimisega ja selle alusel teatatakse riskidest asutuse n&otilde;ukogule; </eesti>
<inglise> (ii) the institution has a risk control unit that is independent from business trading units and reports directly to senior management. </inglise>
<eesti> ii) asutusel on kauplemisosakondadest s&otilde;ltumatu riskij&auml;relevalve osakond, kes annab aru otse n&otilde;ukogule. </eesti>
<inglise> The unit must be responsible for designing and implementing the institution's risk-management system. </inglise>
<eesti> Osakond peab vastutama asutuse riskijuhtimiss&uuml;steemi kavandamise ja rakendamise eest. </eesti>
<inglise> It shall produce and analyse daily reports on the output of the risk-measurement model and on the appropriate measures to be taken in terms of trading limits; </inglise>
<eesti> Ta koostab ja anal&uuml;&uuml;sib iga p&auml;ev aruandeid riskim&otilde;&otilde;tmismudeliga saadud tulemuste ja kauplemise piirm&auml;&auml;radega seotud asjakohaste meetmete kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> (iii) the institution's board of directors and senior management are actively involved in the risk-control process and the daily reports produced by the risk-control unit are reviewed by a level of management with sufficient authority to enforce both reductions of positions taken by individual traders as well as in the institution's overall risk exposure; </inglise>
<eesti> iii) asutuse juhatus ja n&otilde;ukogu osalevad aktiivselt riskij&auml;relevalves ning riskij&auml;relevalve osakonna koostatud p&auml;evaaruanded vaatab l&auml;bi selline juhtimistasand, kellel on piisavad volitused v&auml;hendada nii &uuml;ksikute kauplejate v&otilde;etud positsioone kui ka asutuse koguriski; </eesti>
<inglise> (iv) the institution has sufficient numbers of staff skilled in the use of sophisticated models in the trading, risk-control, audit and back-office areas; </inglise>
<eesti> iv) asutustel on piisav hulk t&ouml;&ouml;tajaid, kes oskavad kasutada keerulisi mudeleid kauplemisel, riskij&auml;relevalves, kontrollimisel ja tehingute arveldamisel; </eesti>
<inglise> (v) the institution has established procedures for monitoring and ensuring compliance with a documented set of internal policies and controls concerning the overall operation of the risk-measurement system; </inglise>
<eesti> v) asutus on kehtestanud riskim&otilde;&otilde;tmiss&uuml;steemi &uuml;ldist toimimist k&auml;sitlevate kirjalike asutusesiseste tegevus- ja kontrollip&otilde;him&otilde;tete t&auml;itmise j&auml;relevalve ja tagamise korra; </eesti>
<inglise> (vi) the institution's models have a proven track record of reasonable accuracy in measuring risks; </inglise>
<eesti> vi) on olemas kinnitatud andmed, et asutuse mudelitega on riske piisavalt t&auml;pselt m&otilde;&otilde;detud; </eesti>
<inglise> (vii) the institution frequently conduct a rigorous programme of stress testing and the results of these tests are reviewed by senior management and reflected in the policies and limits it sets; </inglise>
<eesti> vii) asutus rakendab tihti ranget kriisitestimiskava, mille tulemused vaatab n&otilde;ukogu l&auml;bi ja v&otilde;tab neid oma kinnitatavates tegevusp&otilde;him&otilde;tetes ja piirm&auml;&auml;rades arvesse; </eesti>
<inglise> (viii) the institution must conduct, as part of its regular internal auditing process, an independent review of its risk-measurement system. </inglise>
<eesti> viii) asutus peab oma korrap&auml;rase sisekontrolli raames korraldama oma riskijuhtimiss&uuml;steemi s&otilde;ltumatu kontrollimise. </eesti>
<inglise> This review must include both the activities of the business trading units and of the independent risk-control unit. </inglise>
<eesti> Kontrollimine peab h&otilde;lmama nii kauplemisosakondade kui ka s&otilde;ltumatu riskij&auml;relevalve osakonna tegevust. </eesti>
<inglise> At least once a year, the institution must conduct a review of its overall risk-management process. </inglise>
