<eesti> - kontrollimenetlust, mida asutus rakendab mudeli t&auml;psuse m&otilde;&otilde;tmiseks tehtava j&auml;relv&otilde;rdluse hindamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> The institution shall monitor the accuracy and performance of its model by conducting a back-testing programme. </inglise>
<eesti> Asutus kontrollib oma mudeli t&auml;psust ja toimimist j&auml;relv&otilde;rdluskava abil. </eesti>
<inglise> The back-testing has to provide for each business day a comparison of the one-day value-at-risk measure generated by the institution's value by the end of the subsequent business day. </inglise>
<eesti> J&auml;relv&otilde;rdluse abil tuleb iga pangap&auml;eva suhtes v&otilde;rrelda asutuse mudeli p&otilde;hjal j&auml;rgmise pangap&auml;eva l&otilde;puks leitud p&auml;evase riskiv&auml;&auml;rtuse &otilde;igsust. </eesti>
<inglise> Competent authorities shall examine the institution's capability to perform back-testing on both actual and hypothetical changes in the portfolio's value. </inglise>
